C401 [*] Unnecessary generator (rewrite as a set comprehension)
 --> C401_py315.py:3:1
  |
1 | xs = [[1], [2]]
2 |
3 | set(*x for x in xs)
  | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  |
help: Rewrite as a set comprehension
1 | xs = [[1], [2]]
2 |
  - set(*x for x in xs)
3 + {*x for x in xs}
note: This is an unsafe fix and may change runtime behavior
